        "html": "=<div style=\"background:#f4f4f4;padding:2rem;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;\">\n\n    <div style=\"background:#0f172a;padding:24px 32px;\">\n      <span style=\"color:#ffffff;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;\">rbcode.xyz</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"padding:32px;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#15803d;\">¡Pago confirmado!</p>\n        <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#16a34a;\">Tu pedido ha sido procesado exitosamente.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:14px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.6;\">\n        Hola <strong>{{ $json.customerName }}</strong>, recibimos tu pago correctamente. Aquí tienes el resumen:\n      </p>\n\n      <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n        <table style=\"width:100%;font-size:13px;border-collapse:collapse;\">\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"color:#94a3b8;padding:4px 0;\">Número de orden</td>\n            <td style=\"color:#0f172a;font-weight:600;text-align:right;font-family:monospace;\">{{ $json.orderId }}</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"color:#94a3b8;padding:4px 0;\">ID de pago MP</td>\n            <td style=\"color:#0f172a;font-weight:600;text-align:right;font-family:monospace;\">{{ $json.mpPaymentId }}</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"color:#94a3b8;padding:4px 0;\">Fecha de pago</td>\n            <td style=\"color:#0f172a;font-weight:600;text-align:right;\">{{ $json.paidAtFormatted }}</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td style=\"color:#94a3b8;padding:4px 0;\">Estado</td>\n            <td style=\"text-align:right;\">\n              <span style=\"background:#f0fdf4;color:#15803d;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;\">{{ $json.paymentStatus }}</span>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#0f172a;\">Detalle de items</p>\n\n      <table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:8px;\">\n        <tr>\n          <th style=\"text-align:left;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;padding-bottom:8px;font-weight:500;\">Cant.</th>\n          <th style=\"text-align:left;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;padding-bottom:8px;font-weight:500;\">Precio unit.</th>\n          <th style=\"text-align:right;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;padding-bottom:8px;font-weight:500;\">Subtotal</th>\n        </tr>\n        {{ $json.itemsHtml }}\n      </table>\n\n      <div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 0;border-top:2px solid #0f172a;margin-top:8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;\">Total pagado</p>\n        <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#15803d;\">{{ $json.currency }} {{ $json.total }}</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <p style=\"margin:24px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;text-align:center;\">\n        Si tienes alguna consulta sobre tu pedido, contáctanos en soporte@rbcode.xyz\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background:#f8fafc;padding:16px 32px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94a3b8;text-align:center;\">© 2025 rbcode.xyz · Todos los derechos reservados</p>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
